title: Orbiter (2003) (digital-Empire)
description:
Promotional info - "Written by Warren Ellis; art and cover by Colleen Doran A stunning softcover edition of Warren Ellis's and Colleen Doran's acclaimed original VERTIGO graphic novel. When a space shuttle crash lands on Earth after being missing for a decade, it unlocks a mystery that will unfold deep in outer space. Can a team of three specialists cheated out of their dream of spaceflight discover the nature of this bizarre space-borne anomaly?"

Obviously this is not a physical softcover edition, lol, but the newly released digital version by Empire. Thanks to them for their efforts, please seed and enjoy! :-)
